sequenceDiagram
    participant FW as FW DVFS FSM
    participant PMIC as PMIC/Regulator
    participant CLK as Clock/CRG
    participant PLL as PLL
    participant GPU as GPGPU Domain

    FW->>GPU: request idle/drain or active-change permission
    GPU-->>FW: safe ack
    FW->>PMIC: set voltage if target freq higher
    PMIC-->>FW: voltage stable
    FW->>CLK: switch domain to safe clock / bypass
    CLK-->>FW: safe clock ack
    FW->>PLL: write refdiv/fbdiv/postdiv/enable
    PLL-->>FW: pll_lock
    FW->>CLK: select PLL output and divider
    CLK-->>FW: clock switch ack
    FW->>PMIC: lower voltage if target freq lower
    PMIC-->>FW: voltage stable
    FW->>FW: update current OPP/freq and release lock
